author: Derek Bayne
title: Keith volleyball clinches conference title
text:
Keith volleyball clinches conference title Posted: dbayne@wrex.com ROCKFORD (WREX) - 
Keith Country Day's volleyball team adds another piece of hardware to its growing collection. The Lady Cougars knocked off Harvest Christian from Elgin to win the Northeastern Athletic Conference title. 
Harvest Christian features South Carolina commit Mikayla Robinson, the daughter of former Chicago Bear Marcus Robinson. 
Keith's Zoe Nunez, a Notre Dame commit, helped the Lady Cougars win in straight sets. Keith celebrated its Senior Night before the game. Can't Find Something? 10322 Auburn Road, Rockford, IL 61103 Switchboard: 815-335-2213
